    <string name="onboarding_optional_profile">Optionally, tell us about yourself on the next screens. This stays on your device and helps generate noise that\'s different from your real profile. Skip if you prefer uniform noise.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_done_title">You\'re set!</string>
    <string name="onboarding_done_body">Fauxx will generate diverse browsing activity that\'s maximally different from your real behavioral signal. Toggle protection on from the Dashboard to start.</string>
